{"tid":1368482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務人員不可發出匿名信件 不得就任何事宜直接致函政務司司長","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:40:29.000Z","uid":36811,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8de2debb214edb7671ea6e2154f8a879eb3f15b","tid":1368482,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:25:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo006.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo006.pdf&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07itC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=f2e536ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo006.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n警察通例<br />\n<br />\n第 6 章 行為及紀律<br />\n<br />\n22. 警務人員不可發出匿名信件，此舉可被視為有損警隊良好秩序及紀律的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo012.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo012.pdf&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07itC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=d353583d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo012.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n警察通例<br />\n<br />\n第 12 章 文書處理與辦公室實務<br />\n<br />\n12-06 與其他政府部門及外間機構通信<br />\n除《警察通例》第 27 章或《程序手冊》第 12 章另有規定外，警務人員(職 務所需者除外)不得就任何事宜直接致函行政長官、政務司司長、政府總部局長級官員或 部門首長。有關信件須經由警務處處長轉交。"},{"pid":"0ac7c28c03b0786d85057749836cbe2bf1ec8c05","tid":1368482,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fe6858a2079d11d94b23db56f929e8ec1367d2","tid":1368482,"uid":82947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"所以佢哋出公開信囉<br />\n<br />\n唔好寫錯收信人名啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fe0bc8da455f1974671ac1312c78690883823e","tid":1368482,"uid":272243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"軍伐嘛 邊有皇法呢"},{"pid":"8957d9c80ee3e1657cde0d31a858f12065bac590","tid":1368482,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"算喇 警方通例如同廢紙一樣 <br />\n冇人識冇人理嘅<br />\n分分鐘連登仔呢排睇通例識得仲多過黑警"},{"pid":"2f5ea507fda3c9d642cebf2dbb75bc111ca1f59a","tid":1368482,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cb6da608bd098580edf56ae310a76cba7de255","tid":1368482,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"犯晒<br />\n警察通例唔係法例<br />\n而家啲點警返國內接受精英訓練<br />\n精通目無法紀 共產黨萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}